Class MockContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.agorapulse.gru.agp.MockContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.amazonaws.services.lambda.runtime.Context

    public class MockContext
extends Object
implements com.amazonaws.services.lambda.runtime.Context
    A simple mock implementation of the Context interface. Default values are stubbed out, and setters are provided so you can customize the context before passing it to your function.
